channel.title: Blank Deltascape Source and Client?
channel.description:
Hello, sorry if you don't like requests. I had a clean Deltascape Source and Client and my brother deleted the bloody files. The link which I try to use is unavailable because it's MegaUpload. Could someone give me the link to a completed cleaned one, e.g. no customs, no shitty interface (different colours). I have actually looked all over the web but have found nothing which is completely clean, or it is just the source.
Cheers.
